    participant User as Developer
    participant API as API Layer (Spring Boot)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (State)
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ (Queue)
    participant Build as Build Engine (Worker)
    participant Cluster as Runtime Cluster (K8s)
    participant Kaniko as Build Tool (Kaniko)
    participant Registry as Image Registry

    Note over User,Registry: === DEPLOYMENT INITIALIZATION ===
    
    User->>API: POST /api/apps/{id}/deploy
    API->>DB: Create Build Record (QUEUED)
    API->>MQ: Publish BuildRequestedEvent
    API-->>User: 202 Accepted {buildId}
    
    Note over User,Registry: === BUILD & PACKAGING ===
    
    MQ->>Build: Consume Build Event
    Build->>DB: Update Build (BUILDING)
    Build->>Cluster: Create Build Pod (Kaniko)
    
    loop Log Streaming
        Kaniko->>Build: Stream Logs
        Build-->>User: WebSocket (Live Logs)
    end
    
    Kaniko->>Registry: Push Image Artifact
    Build->>DB: Update Build (SUCCESS)
    
    Note over User,Registry: === RUNTIME DEPLOYMENT ===
    
    Build->>Cluster: Apply K8s Manifests
    Build->>DB: Create Deployment (HEALTHY)
    Cluster-->>User: App reachable at: [url]
